---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Roadmap | Superior"
  description="Release ladder for Superior: learn and shadow now, one tightly capped Kalshi starter bot next."
>
  <section class="machine-page">
    <header class="machine-page__header">
      <div class="machine-page__title">
        <span class="machine-page__label">Roadmap</span>
        <strong>Starter bot / release ladder</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="machine-page__status">SHADOW / ARM / AUTO</div>
    </header>

    <div class="machine-page__body machine-page__body--single">
      <div class="machine-page__column">
        <div class="machine-page__block">
          <span>Current shape</span>
          <strong>Learn the route. Clear shadow. Arm one starter bot.</strong>
          <p>Ship one narrow Kalshi autopilot path first. Add breadth only after the trust model feels solid.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="machine-page__rail">
          <article class="machine-page__strip">
            <span class="machine-page__strip-label">Now</span>
            <div class="machine-page__strip-body">
              <strong>Trust ramp</strong>
              <p>Learn chapters, shadow clears, visible caps, and a local activity log that explains why the bot would act.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="machine-page__strip">
            <span class="machine-page__strip-label">Next</span>
            <div class="machine-page__strip-body">
              <strong>Kalshi starter bot</strong>
              <p>One venue, one internal-binary strategy family, one risk envelope, one visible kill switch.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="machine-page__strip">
            <span class="machine-page__strip-label">Later</span>
            <div class="machine-page__strip-body">
              <strong>Deeper trust features</strong>
              <p>Crash recovery, stronger audit views, and tighter venue health checks once the single live lane is stable.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="machine-page__strip">
            <span class="machine-page__strip-label">Not now</span>
            <div class="machine-page__strip-body">
              <strong>No multi-venue live bot</strong>
              <p>No cloud runtime, no Polymarket live path, and no general strategy builder before one Kalshi lane works.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <nav class="machine-page__controls" aria-label="Roadmap controls">
      <a class="machine-page__control machine-page__control--primary" href="/download/">
        <span>Download</span>
      </a>
      <a class="machine-page__control machine-page__control--secondary" href="/docs/">
        <span>Docs</span>
      </a>
      <a class="machine-page__control machine-page__control--commit" href="https://github.com/Zwin-ux/arbitrage/releases" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
        <span>Releases</span>
      </a>
      <a class="machine-page__control machine-page__control--reset" href="https://github.com/Zwin-ux/arbitrage" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
        <span>GitHub</span>
      </a>
    </nav>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
